1. Project Overview

You are building the main corporate website for a company that operates in multiple business sectors and has multiple branch locations.
	•	Framework: Astro (with Content Collections + MDX enabled)
	•	Focus: SEO-friendly, fully mobile responsive, lightning-fast website
	•	Design: Provided via Figma MCP → Cursor must implement layouts/components following Figma class names
	•	Hosting: Vercel (SSG)
	•	No dynamic server logic – site must be static where possible, only light interactivity (Astro Islands)
    
