3. Content Collections

Sectors

Each sector represents a business line (e.g., Restaurants, Construction, Cleaning).
src/content/sectors/*.mdx

Fields:
	•	title (string)
	•	slug (string)
	•	summary (short description shown on detail page)
	•	heroImage (string, optional)
	•	gallery (array of images)
	•	seo (title, description, image optional)

Locations

Each location represents a branch of the company.
src/content/locations/*.mdx

Fields:
	•	city (string)
	•	branch (string)
	•	address (string)
	•	phone (string, optional)
	•	email (string, optional)
	•	coords (lat, lng optional)
	•	hours (array of { day, open, close })
	•	images (array of strings)
	•	sectorRefs (array of sector slugs)
	•	seo (title, description)

