4. Pages

Homepage (index.astro)
	•	Lists all sectors using SectorCard components
	•	Each card links to /sectors/[slug]

Sector Page (/sectors/[slug])

Sections:
	1.	Hero: Title, summary, heroImage
	2.	Gallery: grid of gallery images
	3.	Locations Section: filtered list of all branches that include this sector (sectorRefs)
	•	For each location:
	•	Name (city + branch)
	•	Address + phone/email links
	•	Opening hours
	•	Google Maps embed (iframe, lazy-loaded)
	•	“Get Directions” button linking to Google Maps
	4.	SEO: JSON-LD Service schema for the sector

Location Page (/locations/[city]/[branch])
	•	Branch details: title, address, phone/email, working hours
	•	Gallery of branch images
	•	Google Maps embed (iframe, lazy)
	•	Services (sectorRefs) linked back to sector pages
	•	JSON-LD LocalBusiness schema

About & Contact Pages
	•	About: static markdown or MDX page
	•	Contact: static form (no JS, use Netlify Forms or Formspree) + contact info

