6. SEO Rules
	•	Global <head>: meta title, description, OG tags, Twitter tags, canonical
	•	Sitemap & Robots via @astrojs/sitemap
	•	JSON-LD:
	•	Organization on homepage
	•	Service on sector pages
	•	LocalBusiness on location pages
	•	BreadcrumbList JSON-LD on sectors & locations
	•	Images: always include alt, preload LCP image

⸻

7. Performance Rules
	•	Astro Islands only when necessary (prefer static HTML)
	•	All images optimized using @astrojs/image
	•	Fonts self-hosted, display=swap
	•	Maps via <iframe> embeds, not heavy JS libraries
	•	Lazy-load iframes and galleries
	•	Lighthouse performance ≥ 95

